    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Rooms provided for eating meals, particularly at a work place, school, or other such establishment where many people spend the day away from home; the the food is often brought from elsewhere, but prepared food may also be offered for sale.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
